//i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F115415_3327080fbf689962ab5fd097785c53cf.jpg&h=8336c7e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/115418_971ae695bdd79d9b2a2b8217a05e8c79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F115418_971ae695bdd79d9b2a2b8217a05e8c79.jpg&h=67258621&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/115423_6d93d7c88f73cfccf78bc0ba91fa794b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F115423_6d93d7c88f73cfccf78bc0ba91fa794b.jpg&h=cf91ebee&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾點開始上山<br />\n<br />\nCHUR唔CHUR?</blockquote><br />\n如果御來光館cancel我booking<br />\n我都會彈丸上山<br />\n係唔知要幾點開始行</blockquote><br />\n唔chur，果日我夜晚7點半開始行，11點幾到達八合目太子館，之後係出面休息左兩個鐘，凌晨1點幾再開始攻頂，4點左右就到山頂，就到山頂果陣基本係塞晒車，勁多人<br />\n如果想彈丸登山我建議果日山頂天氣要好好先得，我果日就係天氣勁好，冇咩風同冇落雨，好順利就登頂"},{"pid":"aac7e522cecfbc616afc95bd5b1f5df485cbd693","tid":285071,"uid":86487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:41:09.000Z","msg":"御來光館垃圾黎，d床位逼到狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n未book 既話建議你係低少少既地方休息早少少出發"},{"pid":"744e9262aef9a1e03b1b40f52a0e31a00ae533e7","tid":285071,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:42:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>御來光館垃圾黎，d床位逼到狗也不屌<br />\n<br />\n未book 既話建議你係低少少既地方休息早少少出發</blockquote><br />\n專比外國人住係咁上下啦"},{"pid":"df5484e3783bfed4d2d3b37b97b8f74fd2e06575","tid":285071,"uid":28823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T07:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無知一問 其實上富士山 係有無得登山 or上頂  山上有啲咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 真係無咩深入了解過</blockquote><br />\n除左7-8月，富士山五合目(山腰)會開<br />\n再上就係雪山，如果要上好似要申請<br />\n到左7月頭就會開山比人上<br />\n山屋都會開放比人住<br />\n到左大約7月1x號，山頂劍峰都會開埋<br />\n山上主要睇御來光(姐係日出)<br />\n不過係起全日本最高海拔地方睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr